Package: lantern
Version: 0.1.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd, sudo, libnotify4, libnss3, libxtst6, libgtk-3-0, libgbm1, libasound2, libxss1
Recommends: caddy, dnsmasq
Maintainer: Lantern <lantern@localhost>
Description: Local development environment manager
 Lantern is a Valet-like development environment manager for Linux.
 It includes a daemon (systemd service), a CLI tool, and a desktop app.
 After installation the daemon runs on port 4777, the `lantern` CLI is
 available in PATH, and the desktop app appears in your application menu.
